This paper deals with the use of deep neural networks (DNNs) in autonomous systems, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning (RL) and navigation, which suggests the categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision (CV) for pedestrian detection, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with safety-critical applications, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
